{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_06_02",
  "title": "kana 2話 山田、サボるなー！！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。それじゃ、MV撮影に向けての\nミーティングをはじめまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. Then let's begin the meeting\nfor the MV shooting~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "何か意見ある人ー\nはい、{user}さん早かった。どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyone have opinions~\nYes‚ {user}-san was quick. Go ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あの、franさんとmihoさんは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ where are fran-san and miho-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "呼んでない。franはどうせ「新曲が売れたら\nそこから補填すればいいじゃない」としか言わないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't call them. fran would just say \"If the new song sells‚\nwe can just cover the costs with that.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "mihoは「映像は専門外だから任せる」ってさ\nで？　ちゃんとアイデア考えてきたんでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And miho said \"Video isn't my specialty so I'll leave it to you.\"\nSo? You did come up with some ideas‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲作りに密着した映像が丸ごとある訳ですし\nそれをもらって、音楽に合わせて加工すれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we have full footage of the new song’s creation‚\nif we take that and edit it to match the music…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "却下。メイキング映像はあくまでおまけなんだから\nそっちを本編にしてどうすんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rejected. Making-of footage is just a bonus.\nWhat's the point of making that the main feature?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "だいたい、夏に思い切り弾けましょうって曲なのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ it's a song about really letting loose in summer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.9000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "あのバカどもと顔つき合わせて曲作ってるとこなんて\n最悪な夏じゃん。曲との温度差が酷過ぎて風邪引くわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But making the song while facing those idiots?\nThat's the worst summer. The mood gap is so bad I might catch a cold.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0999977112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "じ……じゃあ、さくら達にも出演してもらうというのは\n頼めば出てくれるでしょうし、ギャラは要相談で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-then how about having Sakura and the others appear too?\nIf we ask they'd probably do it‚ and we can negotiate the fee…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ボツ。あのね、内輪で盛り上がってるだけのMVなんて\n一番、寒いやつでしょうが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Scrapped. Listen‚ an MV that's just us getting hyped among ourselves?\nThat's the lamest kind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "ったく、ポンコツマネージャーから\n使える案が出てくると思ったのが間違いだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ expecting anything useful\nfrom a useless manager was my mistake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱ、あんたじゃなくて\nkanaが監督やらないと駄目か～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess it's not you\nbut kana who has to be the director~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "と、言いますと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what do you mean…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1333244325,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6700.0089008,
          "startTime": 93.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "しょうがないから、kanaが一肌脱いでやるってこと\nはい、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can't be helped‚ so kana'll roll up her sleeves.\nHere‚ this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4030902387,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1663.5700701999951,
          "startTime": 95.0666603089
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "この書類は……ええと、動画の絵コンテですかね？\n長さは四分半……あ、もしかして新曲の？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This document is… um‚ a video storyboard?\nThe length is four and a half minutes… oh‚ could this be for the new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4000025431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "あんただけに任せたら、永遠に新曲出せなそうだから\nkanaがかわりに考えてきてやったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I left it just to you‚ we'd never be able to release the new song\nso kana thought it up instead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8666692097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "kana、SNS用の動画は自分で編集してるし\nぶっちゃけ、そこらのフリーランスよりうまいからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana edits videos for SNS herself\nand honestly‚ she's better than most freelancers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6666671752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに……この絵コンテに沿って撮れれば\nかなりいいMVが出来そうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true… if we can shoot following this storyboard\nwe could make a pretty good MV.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8333358764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でもこれ、機材も人もかなり使うプランですよね\n予算がないのがそもそもの問題なのに、どうやって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this plan needs a lot of equipment and people‚ right?\nThe lack of budget is the problem to begin with‚ so how…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.866670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "ん。だから友達に頼むつもり。エキストラの役とかさ\nあとkanaの友達、映像に詳しい奴も何人かいるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mm. So I’m planning to ask my friends. For things like extra roles.\nPlus‚ kana has several friends who know a lot about video.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.266670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "何よ。あんたが役に立たないから\nかわりにkanaの人脈駆使してんのよ、感謝してよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know what? Because you're useless‚\nkana's using her connections instead. Be grateful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5333358764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "ロケ地はまぁ、この間のプールまた借りればいいでしょ\nあそこ、結構雰囲気良かったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For the location… Well‚ we can just borrow that pool from before.\nThat place had pretty good atmosphere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.7666692097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaさんの友達か……助かるんだけど）\n（どんな人達なんだろう。いまいち想像がつかないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（kana-san's friends… it's helpful but）\n（what kind of people are they? I can't really imagine）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.9333358764,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7266.6575131,
          "startTime": 174.1999933895
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――MV Shooting Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9000025431,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1266.657511300025,
          "startTime": 174.1666600544
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 174.0666600544
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 174.0666600544
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "げほっ、げほっ……。み、水しぶきを撮りたいからって\n二度もプールに突き落とさないで下さいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cough‚ cough… J-just because you want to film water splashes\nplease don't push me into the pool twice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.9333358764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 184.0999961854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan017.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーなら、新曲発売に命かけて当然でしょ\nまぁ、沈んだら引き上げるくらいはしてやるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're a manager‚ it's just natural to risk your life for the new song release.\nWell‚ if you sink I'll at least pull you up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.5000025431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 192.2333274842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_06_02-kan018.m4a",
      "text": "エキストラ入れたシーンも撮らないといけないんだから\nこんな細かいカットに時間食ってらんないのよ",
